Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.18,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不行 你们要追就必须带上按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说起来葉香的事情才更为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:21.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,回去很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.79,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你们的目的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,夺回葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:24.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:27.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有把世界恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这个好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.75,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,庞太郎本人并没有他想象中的那么聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.24,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,行动很纯粹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,因为很重要所以才会有所隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:35.42,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.21,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:40.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,他不得不抛弃那个重要的按钮而逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不要 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.74,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您无需这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.99,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们已经乘上了「大船」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,担心 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那些不讲道理的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.07,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不讲道理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:56.94,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.49,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,他们那群人是会威胁到公主的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.10,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,所以请您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.60,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我庞太郎会一心一意 努力工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.34,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那么我现在就去确认一下状况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.37,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主像往常一样生活就可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.72,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.56,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,往常是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.68,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,睡觉 起床 吃饭 学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,然后是 谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,刚刚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,快来 你不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:31.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,所以说那个按钮也有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,会是什么特别的按钮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,除了启动7G以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香和按钮两者缺一不可 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对啊 组合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.06,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,或许这就是她被称为池袋魔女的缘由了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说葉香按下了按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,按钮给予了葉香力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,然后世界就被改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.08,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.38,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,如果「解铃不是系铃人」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.32,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,开启按钮的中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.36,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,需要她再按一次关闭按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:10.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,这恐怕是让世界和中富葉香恢复如初的唯一办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 道路分叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 走 走哪条路为好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 哪条哪条
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 波奇它知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不愧是波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.74,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,最近的都好难对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你要是不好好当个人偶我可就犯难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.23,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,纠缠不休的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是我 你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,给老子快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 前方危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.25,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 这距离根本听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.35,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,难道我会坐以待毙把公主拱手让出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 啥鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:57.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们去到对面的车上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:05:59.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但但但但是但是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:02.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:04.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.75,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:15.50,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果万一回到之前 肯定要追究7G的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.15,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这种事情绝对不能发生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊 终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.62,ZH-Main-Down,Chaos,0,0,0,,毁灭我的国家可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我会马上改变你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,别捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.84,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,把你做成骨办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.42,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,中了的话就会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.40,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.75,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你们这群人都得去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要死的是我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你们对于公主来说毫无存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋和公主是同一的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:14.58,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没有公主就没有池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.65,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,所以没有池袋也就没有公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.59,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.65,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.47,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,把这群家伙全部都揍扁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.09,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我就问一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,没有池袋也就没有公主 是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.81,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,以池袋为中心所放射的7G能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.11,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是以她为中心所产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.07,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,不论是否拥有池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.41,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她与池袋都是「同生」的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,这会削减葉香大人的寿命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,削减
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.86,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,人终究要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.05,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而她的死支撑起了池袋这一伟业 有何不满
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.93,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,那这是葉香大人的意愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.83,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你是不是搞错了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.62,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你不过只是个保镖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是葉香大人的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.16,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,不是你这家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人的痛苦难道不是因为7G造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.79,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是那又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,如果7G停止的话痛苦是否就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,7G让葉香成为了魔女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香也能够「创造」7G的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要按下按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.87,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.46,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不是我们的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只要是关心葉香的都是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样认为可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.13,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.14,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.94,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,博奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.26,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,多半问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香肯定会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是她不明白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这本练爱给她看后肯定就能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.47,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,给她读点涩泽的书说不定也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子姐那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这和葉香没啥关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但为什么带它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香说过自己想像星星一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.30,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啥时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很久之前 在学校花园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香从那时候开始就一直在想着星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我啊 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.15,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你忘了我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,记不起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 我不是来恳求你的原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说起来最坏的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不原谅我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是 我想为我伤害到葉香的行为而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留实际上算是不善言辞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,羞耻感同身受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那本不是我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 虽然有点是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 不是说我是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为我是个笨蛋 所以葉香看起来非常伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但葉香这么厉害 自己却妄自菲薄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 我才会说出难听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 这也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些也是「不可为之」的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在的我才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香生气是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,呐 为什么葉香要攻击静留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香你这样我们不理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,讨厌 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想 想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.71,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「再说了葉香你 不行的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.70,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「牛皮吹太大了也会不好意思的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.37,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,「我根本对葉香你 一无所知啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会 别这样啊葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.85,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,会说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:44.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然这些是我说的 但我也不希望葉香离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在 现在的我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白 我真的明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:51.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「否定他人」总之是一件很过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不论是否已经伤害到了葉香 这些都如鲠在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.18,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,所以你才从吾野出来准备把我接回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.15,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想为我所说过的话而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且 我愿意相信葉香的所行之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想告诉你 我愿意支持你 为你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:12.49,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,自顾自的主张 如此傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:13.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,话太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香 这肯定不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我认为葉香她确实说了些很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但如果这只是傲慢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她根本不会在两年间每天都去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也根本不会来池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊 真的非常辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我没有拜托她 所以毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊 没有拜托我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是若你执意拒绝 葉香也只能「这样下去」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:34.84,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:38.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我以前一直认为这样下去就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一直都在吾野 和葉香还有大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以最初我就想找回葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 现在的我才明白这是多么「无趣」的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,很无聊啊 一开始就知道结果是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:54.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,探索未知未解的事物 会越来越有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:59.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听我说 我们从吾野来到池袋这虽然经历了九九八十一难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是经历都非常的有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些全部 都是呆在吾野所不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但就是说 现在的世界是不会变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是「固定的状态」对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真的非常悲催
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且世界好像还在缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我希望改变 想要改变自我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香实际上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.87,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,别一厢情愿说自己是「真心」的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在你快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.17,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,并不 快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,并不快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野发生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,无论悲伤 还是痛苦 抑或艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 这些都很「快乐」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香 你有一个梦想对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但现在这样什么也不会被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只有把世界恢复如初 才有可能实现梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只要努力就能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,必然有这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再次让世界「运作」起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.81,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.37,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,做不到的话会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,实现不了梦想很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是我 会永远支持葉香的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:59.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为你两肋插刀 在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「不做而后悔」和「做了而后悔」大相径庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我会支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,天狼星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,承诺之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 向着那颗亮晶晶的承诺之星约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,承诺之星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,刚刚给它起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,它的名字应该是叫「天狼星」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:31.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那么 就把它作为我们「承诺」的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.61,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.54,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我根本没有资格成为你所支持之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我一直把静留你当成傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.35,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,话说得很有勇气 却什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.51,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,明明根本做不成什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.08,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,要是一直这样下去 腐朽愚笨下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,被嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,被诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想这不是什么「诅咒」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是「祈愿」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然我一直都呆在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但无论去到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:13.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我都很高兴 你能放下这些「为我的考虑」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:18.00,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,笨蛋 静留你真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,听说我 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起一个人在这 和大家一起更好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那样的话绝对会很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:29.14,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今后的事情 交给今后彼时彼刻的自己考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.53,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,别想按下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.51,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,哈 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.13,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.42,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这可大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不是魔女公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是葉香 中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.31,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,如果世界恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,即便世界无法复原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那时候再考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,乐观主义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这 不也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.72,ZH-Main-Down,Pochi,0,0,0,,葉香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.17,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里是 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:30.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是这样的 还是不是这样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香是这样的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.60,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 和我认知中的葉香匹配度百分百
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,感觉和以前有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.84,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就算河流从同一区域流过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.38,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,所经行的水也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,城市 人们 世界也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.72,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,看似相同 实则不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:55.99,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,一切都在「变化」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又说了这么帅气哲学的总结台词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界也不会完全恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.89,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,变化才是永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.45,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.49,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我要去「确认」这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:10.66,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,有缘再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,诶 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感谢与赞美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,非此即彼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.31,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,可是大家都变回了人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.63,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而是原来由人类变成僵尸的人们 再度变成人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.43,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我还是你们的女王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 这确实很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.82,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,黑木女王 很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.33,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,出发确认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,「远地点号」出发前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.44,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,远地点号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是静留起的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:09.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野 现在怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,难道会不知道怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.01,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,终于联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,果然还是因为7G停止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:28.17,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.14,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.41,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,虽然高兴和不高兴的都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.09,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不如说难以判断的事情同时发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.74,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,全部的影响不能说都消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.84,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,一些 不对 剩下的问题还很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.72,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,把所有人的变化都记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:42.97,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真是真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.33,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,诚大老师可真是用人不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.68,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.53,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,今天的哈吧吧模式比起昨天延长了39秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.92,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,嘛就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.44,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,回家路上要注意好安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.91,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,说不定 这条道路也不会一帆风顺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,有什么东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,其它的线路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,难不成是西武新宿线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,竟然回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那可是新的未知的新宿线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:21.27,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们进入到其它的世界线也是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到底能不能回到吾野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:23.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.33,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,呐 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么你要起「远地点号」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说起来静留这样还挺少见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,毕竟是专业术语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地球与月亮 相隔最远的地方就是「远地点」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那么之后 便是「靠近」了
Comment: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:52.70,JP-ED-Up,,0,0,0,,ED-JP
