Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:27.24,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}倾雨侵润　无伞无依
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.16,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}诸行万事　漠不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:34.91,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}微弱光斑　耀眼可怖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:38.83,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不是小菜一碟吗　不是问题不大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:43.59,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}同行步伐　已然厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.88,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}但我不想　孑然一身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.18,ZH-ED-Down-side,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}四目相对　呆若木鸡
